00:09:56.883 --> 00:09:59.100
JOHN WATERS: That's about
as spiritual as I get.

00:09:59.100 --> 00:10:01.140
I do believe in the
basic goodness of people.

00:10:01.140 --> 00:10:04.510
There are people that are
born wired wrong, though, yes.

00:10:04.510 --> 00:10:07.105
But I have faith in people.

00:10:07.105 --> 00:10:08.250
I taught in prison.

00:10:08.250 --> 00:10:09.970
I can get along with
all kinds of people.

