fuck me in an Easter basket

00:10:22.465 --> 00:10:23.740
on Easter morning.

00:10:23.740 --> 00:10:27.010
Why do they tell me that?

00:10:27.010 --> 00:10:28.912
Because I'll understand.

00:10:28.912 --> 00:10:32.054
[LAUGHTER]

00:10:32.054 --> 00:10:33.720
MALE SPEAKER 1: I
mean, isn't it so much

00:10:33.720 --> 00:10:35.386
more interesting to
talk to those people

00:10:35.386 --> 00:10:37.776
than, you know-- us?

00:10:37.776 --> 00:10:38.442
JOHN WATERS: No.

00:10:38.442 --> 00:10:41.100
No, because-- I never understand
people say they're bored.

00:10:41.100 --> 00:10:42.704
Well, walk outside
and look at people.

00:10:42.704 --> 00:10:43.370
I'm never bored.

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:46.000
That's the one thing I
never am, because I'm

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:47.530
interested in human behavior.

00:10:47.530 --> 00:10:50.210
And the most that I
made the movies about

00:10:50.210 --> 00:10:51.700
and that I wrote
about are people

00:10:51.700 --> 00:10:54.930
that think they're normal
but, to me, are really insane.

00:10:54.930 --> 00:10:56.305
Because most of
the people I know

00:10:56.305 --> 00:10:58.760
in New York who think
they're insane are actually

00:10:58.760 --> 00:10:59.975
kind of normal.

00:10:59.975 --> 00:11:03.470
So it's always weird
how people conceive

00:11:03.470 --> 00:11:05.410
of themselves and
their own beliefs.

00:11:05.410 --> 00:11:08.780
MALE SPEAKER 2: Did you find
any of that on the road-- people

00:11:08.780 --> 00:11:14.020
that were more-- Were
people more insane

00:11:14.020 --> 00:11:16.486
than you thought they
would be, or less?

00:11:16.486 --> 00:11:17.950
JOHN WATERS: They were neither.

00:11:17.950 --> 00:11:20.510
I don't know that I
thought they'd be insane.

00:11:20.510 --> 00:11:23.480
The people were-- I did
not get a scary ride.

00:11:23.480 --> 00:11:25.980
I didn't even get one
that was a bad driver.

00:11:25.980 --> 00:11:28.797
I got 21 rides, it took.

00:11:28.797 --> 00:11:29.630
I got a coal miner--

00:11:29.630 --> 00:11:31.505
MALE SPEAKER 1: That
sounds surprisingly low.

00:11:31.505 --> 00:11:34.244
JOHN WATERS: Well, one
big character in the book,

00:11:34.244 --> 00:11:35.439
the Karate Kid--

00:11:35.439 --> 00:11:36.689
MALE SPEAKER 1: The Corvette--

00:11:36.689 --> 00:11:38.650
JOHN WATERS: Corvette Kid.

00:11:38.650 --> 00:11:40.437
