in the pouring rain

00:11:44.310 --> 00:11:46.450
when he was going to get
his lunch at the Subway.

00:11:46.450 --> 00:11:48.931
He didn't know who I was,
even after I told him.

00:11:48.931 --> 00:11:50.020
We just kept talking.

00:11:50.020 --> 00:11:51.510
He drove me all the way to Ohio.

00:11:51.510 --> 00:11:53.080
His parents were,
like, horrified.

00:11:53.080 --> 00:11:53.890
Where is he?

00:11:53.890 --> 00:11:55.390
And looked up John Waters.

00:11:55.390 --> 00:11:57.340
It's not good if you Google me.

00:11:57.340 --> 00:11:58.280
It's bad.

00:11:58.280 --> 00:11:59.690
[LAUGHTER]

00:11:59.690 --> 00:12:02.280
