Manson family, you know?

00:12:02.280 --> 00:12:03.490
Like, oh, great!

00:12:03.490 --> 00:12:06.460
My kid's with him.

00:12:06.460 --> 00:12:07.940
And then he went back.

00:12:07.940 --> 00:12:09.760
