00:12:14.950 --> 00:12:16.330
and caught up with me in Denver.

00:12:16.330 --> 00:12:17.650
So he was great.

00:12:17.650 --> 00:12:18.330
We just had a--

00:12:18.330 --> 00:12:19.322
MALE SPEAKER 1: And you
met him in Baltimore.

00:12:19.322 --> 00:12:21.738
JOHN WATERS: I didn't meet
him-- oh, afterwards I met him.

00:12:21.738 --> 00:12:22.790
But I didn't know him.

00:12:22.790 --> 00:12:24.400
MALE SPEAKER 1: But that's
where he first picked you up--

00:12:24.400 --> 00:12:25.666
JOHN WATERS: We met
in Millersville.

00:12:25.666 --> 00:12:26.582
It was the third ride.

00:12:26.582 --> 00:12:28.534
Which is about an hour
outside of Baltimore.

00:12:28.534 --> 00:12:30.577
I didn't even know
what Millersville was.

00:12:30.577 --> 00:12:32.702
MALE SPEAKER 1: It kind of
reminded me of the scene

00:12:32.702 --> 00:12:35.120
in "The Jerk" when you
