00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:36.490
I think with the first
guy took you, like,

00:12:36.490 --> 00:12:37.520
down the block or something.

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:38.980
JOHN WATERS: Well,
the first ride

00:12:38.980 --> 00:12:42.445
