a Whole Foods jail.

00:15:14.426 --> 00:15:16.250
You know that look.

00:15:16.250 --> 00:15:19.102
MALE SPEAKER 1: Are we ever
going to see that film?

00:15:19.102 --> 00:15:22.340
What's the state of low-budget,
independent film right now?

00:15:22.340 --> 00:15:23.860
JOHN WATERS: Oh, it's bad.

00:15:23.860 --> 00:15:27.240
I mean TV is better now.

00:15:27.240 --> 00:15:28.730
More people see it.

00:15:28.730 --> 00:15:32.330
