00:38:24.326 --> 00:38:25.450
Don't wink at the audience.

00:38:25.450 --> 00:38:28.827
Say it like you believe every
line is completely true.

00:38:28.827 --> 00:38:30.410
That's why I, except
for Tracy Ullman,

00:38:30.410 --> 00:38:33.227
